{"tid":11145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國羽毛球賽冠軍獎座未頒先碎！！！","createTime":"2016-11-29T07:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T10:18:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa4d681c4467edeffbf4b7cb63cd614a8ea1f42","tid":11145,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161124/s00004/1480001056368SL4_075EEF866F4D446FA189A5E7DE13EEB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161124%2Fs00004%2F1480001056368SL4_075EEF866F4D446FA189A5E7DE13EEB5.jpg&h=5836bc10&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早前舉行的中國羽毛球公開賽中，奧運金牌得主諶龍不敵丹麥對手約根森屈居亞軍。正當大家都惋惜諶龍於主場失落冠軍寶座時，頒獎台上發生了令人驚愕的小插曲，冠亞軍獎座都在運動員面前斷成兩份，不少網民都諷刺稱，連現在中國製的獎座都開始有「豆腐渣工程」。 <br />\n<br />\n中國羽毛球公開賽男單決賽於本月20日舉行，諶龍出戰丹麥的約根森，以比數是20比22及13比21直落兩局落敗，與冠軍擦身而過。 <br />\n<br />\n不過真正令人尷尬的是後面的頒獎典禮。運動員除了獲得一個紀念圓碟外，還有一座平面羽毛球形狀的水晶座。頒獎嘉賓先頒獎給諶龍，他的水晶座一直相安無事，頒獎嘉賓繼而走到冠軍約根森面前，但遞上水晶座時才驚覺羽毛球的部分不見了，只剩底座，他唯有讓約根森自行拿着斷開的兩部分。 <br />\n<br />\n其時諶龍欲遞上自己的獎座予約根森，希望借其拍照甚至轉贈對方，詎料諶龍在傳遞期間，手中的水晶座亦突然斷開，他眼巴巴看着羽毛球部分掉下，顯得有點不知所措。兩人對望一下後尷尬地離開頒獎台，約根森放下水晶座，諶龍撿回碎裂部分後亦放到台邊，繼續頒獎典禮。 <br />\n<br />\n有網民笑問獎座是否「中國製造」，驚呼：「天啊！這都是什麼豆腐渣」，又替諶龍不值，指「比賽得到的應該是榮譽，不是丟臉」。不過亦有人認為諶龍遞上獎座的行為好比「紳士」，值得一讚。 <br />\n<br />\n（綜合） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161124/s00004/1479997324873SL4_563D2259042517D6FE3AE13766EDEAED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161124%2Fs00004%2F1479997324873SL4_563D2259042517D6FE3AE13766EDEAED.jpg&h=23c18db5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161124/s00004/1479997325450SL4_D43048A203D14CAE314E98557854F615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161124%2Fs00004%2F1479997325450SL4_D43048A203D14CAE314E98557854F615.jpg&h=4829e06e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161124/s00004/1479997325996SL4_9C3D85202BC87355F412183C02A5B097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161124%2Fs00004%2F1479997325996SL4_9C3D85202BC87355F412183C02A5B097.jpg&h=9799e358&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161124/s00004/1479997326558SL4_9CC4DE977A48FBF3924F5086B7C10E8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161124%2Fs00004%2F1479997326558SL4_9CC4DE977A48FBF3924F5086B7C10E8A.jpg&h=cfcefc11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afb0cf0db1d6dd611afd056233d5e2923c3bd8d5","tid":11145,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89298fc48fcb4e5209363a562a2a500681303801","tid":11145,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bc62b33e27b02f8b924d111a82b5a1adbc7a06","tid":11145,"uid":36693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645a367c245b22a389cd94411468844934a395fc","tid":11145,"uid":40607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"符蛤蟈蜻"}]}